description: Warboys is located in Cambridgeshire near the River Ouse and the villages of Somersham, Earith and Bluntisham. This walk from the village takes you along a section of the Pathfinder Long Distance Walk through the countryside to Broughton. Please scroll down for the full list of walks near and around Warboys. The detailed maps below also show a range of footpaths, bridleways and cycle paths in the area.
